::Shadow Wing::

She left her commlink open for the person to respond.
"I am talking through my comm-link.  It allows us to talk to one another 
while being great distances away from each other.  Like, I can talk to you 
from 18 parsecs away with a link like this.  Or even contact someone 5 other 
quatrants away.  I'm so used to it, I hardly notice it.  It's built into my 
arm. It actives when someone uses the maximal frequency.  Or someone can use 
my frequency and talkt to just me. Why? Don't you  have a link?"

Lunarpin smelled the air, his systems were not yet fully online so the
wolf/bot could not hear the incoming transmission Shadow Wing was recieving.
"Who are you talking too?"Lunarpine asked with a puzzled tone to his voice.
"I don't smell anyone nearby. Just an occasional energeon trail diminished
with time."
